        <item>
          <title>Paul Peterson makes PGA Tour debut at age 36 and leaves an impression</title>
          <description><![CDATA[HONOLULU (AP) — The Sony Open is the PGA Tour stop where introductions are in order, and Paul Peterson made quite the first impression. He opened with a 6-under 64 and shared the lead with five others Thursday on a pleasant day at Waialae.]]></description>
